These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  photographer, fisherman, engineer
1. the engineer is on the left of the fisherman##1
2. the engineer is between the photographer and the fisherman##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Job   | photographer | engineer | fisherman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  electrician, scientist, paramedic
1. the electrician is between the scientist and the paramedic##2
2. the scientist is on the right of the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Job   | paramedic | electrician | scientist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, pall-mall, dunhill
1. the pall-mall-smoker is between the siglo-smoker and the dunhill-smoker##2
2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Cigar   | dunhill | pall-mall | siglo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, poppy, balloon-flower
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person who growspoppy and the person who growsorchid##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Flower   | orchid | balloon-flower | poppy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, february, march
1. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in february##2
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Birthday   | february | july | march |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-6::.
