1. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2    |      3      |
| Sport   | soccer | sailing | volleyball |

